    "Name": "Brahma",
    "Details": "Apparently inspired by reports of QuadVees, this version uses an Endo Steel chassis to install tracks in the legs. The chassis swap didn't free enough weight, so this version also removes the jump jets and CASE system of the original. It carries a PPC for firepower.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Variable Range Targeting</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.08</color></b>\n\n<color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limit: Right Lower</color>",
